{"tid":1347203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得個樣既「鐵路應變部隊」原來背囊裝既係薯片、女人底褲","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:54:56.000Z","uid":230104,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac7d05ed86488a7bc8bde597e151eb0b8cdeabc","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcqYO2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcqYO2b.png&h=84546261&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3b9d3bffa38873fab1ebb5564cbf0f99e027bc4","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"全部失蹤"},{"pid":"5713a77551bf430b65726135d1787d834fd08eac","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"搭車記得畀錢呀，尋晚都唔夠料出動，呢支部隊基本上可有可無<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vr4nwhP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVr4nwhP.png&h=9ec70bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4GtrRa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4GtrRa.png&h=0fafa0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmrJfKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmrJfKw.png&h=7da426b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"192422488fe9638c97935f615bae3f723f4ada5e","tid":1347203,"uid":144075,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"成班冇料到既，帶囇背囊以為自己好打得，一有事所謂應變就係潛水，佢老母養大佢地徙曬d米飯"},{"pid":"ef704ace71830ce90b169a9b1215c4ac4c954ee3","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"政府凌晨發聲明回應元朗白衫人亂襲市民一事時，僅輕描淡寫，並將之與上環衝突一同回應，元朗發生的是「聚眾衝突」，上環則有「連番暴力襲警」。 被視為溫和派的國際關係學者沈旭暉在facebook發帖批評，政府新聞處將兩者混為一談，是徹頭徹尾的偷換概念，並認為事件以國際標準必定性為「一場Terrorist Attack（恐怖襲擊）」。<br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉的帖文提到，元朗發生的事件屬於無差別襲擊，完全針對平民；而且遇襲者完全沒有攻擊性，包括老弱婦孺；事件亦維持長達數小時，屬連續、反覆出現的攻擊；而且事件目的是製造公眾無論在任何地方都對個人安全產生的恐慌。但上環則沒有出現上述情況。<br />\n<br />\n他續說，「假如元朗案在世界任何其他地方出現，定義上，這都是一場Terrorist Attack，領袖會定性，嚴查，做一切可做的穩定人心。」他又批評，政府、警方將元朗一事與政治事件混淆，處理元朗的態度，「僅視之為有人受傷的私人糾紛」，慨嘆沒有想過認識的政府中人會變得這樣。"},{"pid":"8b0354c9b45d4a48d79178f80b469cbe38be9c0b","tid":1347203,"uid":268094,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5713a77551bf430b65726135d1787d834fd08eac","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"搭車記得畀錢呀，尋晚都唔夠料出動，呢支部隊基本上可有可無<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vr4nwhP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVr4nwhP.png&h=9ec70bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4GtrRa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4GtrRa.png&h=0fafa0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmrJfKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmrJfKw.png&h=7da426b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"下 炒得啦<br />\n呢件事一隊都無按時到"},{"pid":"073bd62512f2b99f1cd63cc5702939339e1eb630","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27f21580c3d4f4bc20d91b3961787c37f86357c","tid":1347203,"uid":33797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"我仲以為冇人記得党鐵有反恐team<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86faa2db299c09470a3cb7ea92c89c77689624b","tid":1347203,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦而家先岀黎扮野"},{"pid":"542af6833515f788421e3233e90af7ecabe5bce0","tid":1347203,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"支那賤種俾錢攪<br />\n傀儡政權邊敢出聲<br />\n呢埋返屋企打飛機啦黑警"},{"pid":"6dbed9453424dedea7b101f4c959083a42262807","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"元朗區昨晚出現大批手持武器的白衫惡漢，衝入西鐵元朗站見人就打，而警方在接報後久久未有到場平息事件，令不少市民受傷及質疑警隊部署不力。翻查資料，警方於去年12月起成立了一支「鐵路應變部隊」處理港鐵突發事故，由34名警隊精英組成，部分人更來自飛虎隊，於全港93個港鐵車站執行職務，當時更<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曾承諾接報後9分鐘內趕到現場</span></span>。不少網民今日湧到警察facebook專頁相關帖文下留言，質問應變部隊：「你噚晚去咗邊？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n算唔算公職人員行為失當罪？"},{"pid":"540570d049370219567a0650f466d77cbd1bdcc2","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"有無律師講下？"},{"pid":"afc346034448479156e2b822e9d781c53baccb98","tid":1347203,"uid":49609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"冇事扮model ，有事變潛艇"},{"pid":"990da6f9b60110f8b4c700110cd3df521a83165e","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"佢哋演習緊代號「毛能用」既演習，係咪好有型呢？"},{"pid":"64107a9f3bcd1adbe1d495657a249ef6b6a6b660","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"990da6f9b60110f8b4c700110cd3df521a83165e","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"佢哋演習緊代號「毛能用」既演習，係咪好有型呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gz9e95q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgz9e95q.png&h=79210803&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c47ebd2b043cfdc5865b7674b42e3b3cd4a0474e","tid":1347203,"uid":282984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔記得左, 果時岩岩成立巴鳩閉咁"},{"pid":"f44f7be91e7825aede6807adf94a0f3129d5d842","tid":1347203,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47ebd2b043cfdc5865b7674b42e3b3cd4a0474e","tid":1347203,"uid":282984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite